<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1953-08-17T17:52:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1953-08-17T17:52:00-05:00" n="256" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d256">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">330/8–1753: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Mission at the United
                                    Nations</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1953-08-17T18:52:00-04:00">August 17,
                                    1953—6:52 p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>66. Re <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss> election. Since Turk decision to
                            run dependent on indication of success based on preliminary soundings
                            (Ankara’s 189) suggest you approach other delegations on matter working
                            closely with Turkish delegation. Believe <gloss target="#t_UK1">UK</gloss> and France should be approached soonest.</p>
                        <p>While we will of course give Turkey firm support we continue hope it will
                            make real effort develop own candidacy.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_SMITHWB1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Smith</hi>
                                </persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>